programme.desc: Hos Akhmal Nazri dan Atu Zero telah mengembara ke pekan Dungun, Trengganu. Mereka telah menginap di Casa Tanjung Jara, sebuah chalet yang indah dan selesa. Dua hos tersebut mengambil kesempatan untuk menikmati pelbagai makanan laut dan masakan tempatan yang sedap serta melawat tempat-tempat yang indah di pekan ini. Kemudiannya, mereka terus mengembara ke pekan Merang.

programme.title: Superhero Hati S1 Ep11
programme.desc: Dalam episod kali ini, topik yang di sampaikan ialah "Antara Syukur Dan Selesa". Bila kita diberi nikmat kita dituntut untuk bersyukur. Syukur dengan bagaimana? Lebih banyak Allah beri nikmat lebih banyak kita menginfak dan amalan kita. Bersama Ustaz Hassan yang akan mengupas topik ini dengan lebih lanjut lagi.

programme.title: Biar Aku Jadi Penunggu S1 Ep13
programme.desc: Urusan perbincangan ibu bapa Afeet dengan ibu bapa Rafaal untuk menjodohkan Afia dengan Rafaal telah selesai. Hubungan antara Iffat dan Afeet terus berada dengan baiknya, cuma hampir menjadi hambar semula apabila Afeet tercakap yang Iffat akan lebih gembira apabila Rafaal akan menjadi mudah untuk bertemu. Iffat yang hampir merajuk tetapi Afeet sedar kesilapannya dan berjaya memujuk Iffat. Dalam keadaan Rafaal dan Afia, sedang membuat persediaaan untuk hari perkahwinan mereka, Isha masih mengharapkan Rafaal. Isha menemui Iffat, tetapi Iffat tidak menceritakanya. Setelah dia ketahui, Isha marah-marah Iffat, malahan Iffat agak marah apabila Isha mengatakan mudah baginya untuk bertemu Rafaal. Sementara itu Damia kembali dari luar negara. Dia bertemu dengan Atikah, rakan baiknya. Damia selain menceritakan kehidupan sosial negatifnya, masih mengharapkan dia dapat menemui Aqil dan dia juga termaklum bahawa Afeet bertugas di firma guaman bersekali dengan bapa Atikah.

programme.desc: Mengisahkan Rahmat dan Fatimah yang sudah bercerai dan menunjuk-nunjuk antara satu sama lain bahawa mereka boleh mencari pengganti baru.

programme.title: Jalan-Jalan Makan Angin (2019) Ep11
programme.desc: Hos Akhmal Nazri dan Atu Zero membawa penonton ke Nafas Cube @ Mardi, Serdang. Mereka terus memperkenalkan kemudahan sedia ada di tempat penginapan tersebut. Selain daripada mengunjungi G2G Animal Garden untuk mengenali secara lebih rapat pelbagai jenis haiwan, mereka juga melawat House of Kambing untuk menikmati sup kambing yang enak. Aktiviti-aktiviti lain yang dilakukan termasuk melawat Ladang Mini Kelulut untuk merasai manisan madu asli dan menunggang kuda di Majlis Ekuine Malaysia. Seterusnya kedua-dua hos melanjutkan pemgembaraan mereka ke Hotel De Art di USJ 21, Subang Jaya. Hotel berkonsep British ini mempunyai hiasan dalaman yang selesa dan anggun

programme.title: Cinta Tanpa Henti Ep15
programme.desc: Haikal semakin pulih dan terkejut aunty Sally datang menjenguknya. Dia mahu Haikal rahsiakan bahawa dia yang tolak Haikal jatuh tangga. Hasrat Hisyam untuk membeli Warisan Art Gallery terkubur apabila ada pembeli lain membelinya dengan harga yang lebih tinggi. Sumayah@ Maya dapat merasakan kekecewaan suaminya. Dalam diam Maya bertemu Daniel, sepupu Zarif yang membeli galeri tersebut. Mereka adalah rakan kongsi perniagaan. Zarif masih di luar negra dan tidak dapat melupakan Maya. Maya terkejut dan begitu kecewa dengan perbuatan Zarif. Dia luahkan isi hatinya pada Daniel tentang pengorbanan Hisyam. Beberapa hari kemudian, Daniel mahu menjual semula galeri itu pada Hisyam dengan harga 1.9 juta. Hisyam tekad akan berusaha lebih demi mendapatkannya. Sally dan Arman sering bertengkar, Sally nekad untuk bercerai. Dia bertelagah dengan Hajar di pejabat Edruce Airlines. Keesokannya Arman nasihatkan Hajar mencari kerja lain atas saranan Tn Rahim. Arman beritahu Hajar dia akan ceraikan Sally setelah mendapat separuh saham syarikat. Zakiah terdengar rancangan dan kesalahan Arman dan Hajar memesongkan duit syarikat untuk tujuan peribadi. Zakiah memulakan siasatannya. Akibat terlalu tertekan dengan beberapa kejadian yang menimpa Sally, mengambil pil depression. Dia ditemui tersungkur di tepi katil oleh Pn Mahani, disyaki menelan pil berlebihan dos. Kebelakangan ini, Maya kerap mual dan sakit di sekitar rusuk kanan, dia ke klinik mendapatkan nasihat doktor. Doktor mahu jalankan ujian untuk mengenalpasti penyakit Maya.

programme.title: Superhero Hati S1 Ep12
programme.desc: Dalam episod kali ini, topik yang di sampaikan ialah "Antara Syukur Dan Selesa". Bila kita diberi nikmat kita dituntut untuk bersyukur. Syukur dengan bagaimana? Lebih banyak Allah beri nikmat lebih banyak kita menginfak dan amalan kita. Bersama Ustaz Hassan yang akan mengupas topik ini dengan lebih lanjut lagi.

programme.title: Biar Aku Jadi Penunggu S1 Ep14
programme.desc: Iffat telah dua kali terserempak dan dibayangi personali seperti Damia. Iffat menceritakan kepada Afeet. Afeet bersikap biasa setelah mendapat tahu berita itu. Dia sebegitu kerana tidak mahu Iffat terluka atau rasa apa-apa. Sesekali Afeet terkenang semula sikap buruk Damia melayani dan mencercanya dahulu. Lantaran itu, Afeet bertekad dan berazam Damia tidak ada lagi dalam kamusnya. Damia selain dalam keadaan sedang mengandung anak luar nikah, tetapi berselindung dari keluarganya (kandungan masih kecil), dia menanam hasrat akan menemui Aqil, anaknya bersama Affet. Damia juga bercita-cita untuk merosakkan hubungan antara Afeet dengan Iffat. Satu hari Damia datang ke pejabat Afeet, tanpa diundang, Afeet amat marah dan mengusir Damia.

programme.title: Perahu Kertas
programme.desc: Kugy dan Keenan adalah dua sahabat yang punya sifat uniknya masing-masing. Kugy sangat suka curhat di kertas, lalu ia hanyutkan kertasnya ke air. Sementara Keenan suka melukis. Meski punya perbezaan, keduanya sama-sama saling mengagumi dan bahkan jatuh hati pada satu sama lain.

programme.title: J.K.K S5 Ep02
programme.desc: Seluruh penduduk Kampung Kalut mempercayai Wak Gagak (Che Man) setelah dia berjaya menghilangkan kesakitan yang dialami mereka. Suatu hari, Pak Din demam panas. Bijan berkata sekarang semua penduduk sudah tidak perlu risau kalau sakit kerana mereka ada Wak Gagak. Wak Gagak juga turut gunakan kuasa nya untuk pikat hati Lola. Kojack dengan Salman ada menyimpan rasa curiga terhadap Wak Gagak dan mula mengintip pergerakan Wak Gagak. Namun, kehebatan Wak Gagak bukanlah seperti yang disangka. Dia ada kuasa pukau.

programme.title: Selipar Jepun Stileto Merah Ep22
programme.desc: Leto semakin terharu dengan keupayaan dan kesanggupan Stila untuk berubah, demi menyesuaikan diri dalam persekitaran baru itu. Atas sebab itu, dia akhirnya mengambil langkah drastik untuk menguasai kedai bundle itu semula daripada Yani. Datuk Azhar memujuk Stila agar merahsiakan pertemuannya dengan (bekas) perempuan simpanannnya, dengan alasan dia baru saja berbaik dengan Datin Fairuz dan bercadang untuk merujuk semula. Hubungan Yani dan Leto bertambah buruk semula dengan campur tangan Amelia. Dalam suatu pergaduhan, Leto hilang kesabarannya sehingga terpukul Amelia dan menyebabkan dia jatuh pengsan.

programme.title: Cinta Tanpa Henti Ep16
programme.desc: Sumayah@ Maya kdisahkan mengidap Sirosis iaitu kegagalan fungsi hati. Menurut Dr Rohaya, dia perlu segera mendapatkan transplan hati. Maya banyak termenung dan menangis sendirian selepas mengetahui penyakitnya tetapi dia cuba sembunyikan di hadapan Hisyam. Hisyam dapat lihat perubahan sikap isterinya dan semakin lesu. Dia minta Maya berehat dan tak perlu lagi siapkan tempahan. Mahani tahu suaminya sering teringatkan Syifa dan Haikal yang sudah lama tidak datang ke rumah kerana dihalang Maya, akibat kejadian tempoh hari yang terjadi pada Haikal. Mahani pujuk agar Rahim memafkan anak menantunya. Atas kerjasama Saiful mendapatkan bahan bukti kes penyelewengan duit syarikat, akhirnya Hajar dan Arman ditahan pihak polis. Sementara itu, Zakiah dan Saiful bakal mengikat tali pertunangan. Hisyam berjaya mendapatkan semula hak ke atas Warisan Art Gallery. Dia terkejut apabila Daniel memberitahu Maya bertemunya. Sally pula sering bersendirian dibayangi rasa bersalahnya terhadap Maya dulu. Ia adalah karma kerana sikap tamaknya mahu membolot Edruce Airlines. Dia menceritakan segala kebenaran kepada ibunya. Suatu hari, Maya terserempak dengan Zakiah bersama Dr Rohaya ketika hendak membeli barang dan mereka saling mengenali. Ketika Zakiah beredar, Dr Rohaya bertanyakan sebab Maya tidak hadir temujanji dan minta Maya segera dapatkan rawatan lanjut untuk pembedahan pemindahan hati

programme.title: J.K.K S5 Ep02
programme.desc: Seluruh penduduk Kampung Kalut mempercayai Wak Gagak (Che Man) setelah dia berjaya menghilangkan kesakitan yang dialami mereka. Suatu hari, Pak Din demam panas. Bijan berkata sekarang semua penduduk sudah tidak perlu risau kalau sakit kerana mereka ada Wak Gagak. Wak Gagak juga turut gunakan kuasa nya untuk pikat hati Lola. Kojack dengan Salman ada menyimpan rasa curiga terhadap Wak Gagak dan mula mengintip pergerakan Wak Gagak. Namun, kehebatan Wak Gagak bukanlah seperti yang disangka. Dia ada kuasa pukau.

programme.title: BOOM S1 Ep09
programme.desc: Boom Bakat Orang-Orang Muda yang megetegahkan pengarah - pengarah muda yang sedang meningkat naik dan mempersembahkan hasil - hasil karya mereka.

programme.title: Puteri Gunung Ledang S1 Ep15
programme.desc: Natasya hanya berkelulusan SPM tetapi bijak, agak lasak dan adakala lebih bersifat seperti lelaki. Namun sesekali dia berdandan dan bersolek, pastinya kebanyakan pemuda kampung akan terpikat dengan kecantikan yang dimiliki oleh Natasya dan memanggilnya Puteri Gunung Ledang. Natasya berimpian menjadi model terkenal. Setiap kali mencuba nasib, dia gagal dan akhirnya bekerja sebagai kerani di sebuah agensi peragaan sahaja. Nasibnya berubah apabila dia menjadi duta produk kecantikan secara tidak sengaja. Ramai yang mula jatuh hati dan terpikat pada kecantikan Natasya termasuklah majikannya Rayyan. Rayyan seorang lelaki yang kacak tetapi bersikap ‘kaki perempuan’. Mereka berkenalan secara lebih dekat tetapi Natasya meletakkan tujuh syarat untuk membuktikan cintanya

programme.title: Selipar Jepun Stileto Merah Ep22
programme.desc: Leto semakin terharu dengan keupayaan dan kesanggupan Stila untuk berubah, demi menyesuaikan diri dalam persekitaran baru itu. Atas sebab itu, dia akhirnya mengambil langkah drastik untuk menguasai kedai bundle itu semula daripada Yani. Datuk Azhar memujuk Stila agar merahsiakan pertemuannya dengan (bekas) perempuan simpanannnya, dengan alasan dia baru saja berbaik dengan Datin Fairuz dan bercadang untuk merujuk semula. Hubungan Yani dan Leto bertambah buruk semula dengan campur tangan Amelia. Dalam suatu pergaduhan, Leto hilang kesabarannya sehingga terpukul Amelia dan menyebabkan dia jatuh pengsan.

programme.title: Jangan Benci Cintaku Ep02
programme.desc: Shah cuba pujuk Feka supaya menyambung pengajiannya di Kuala Lumpur sahaja. Namun pujuk rayu Shah tidak berjaya.Faris selaku rakan sepejabat itu membuat rancangan supaya Feka tidak jadi menyambung belajar. Faris yang juga baik dengan Feka sengaja menakutkan Feka dengan maklumkan tentang seorang gadis yang telah lama meminati Shah. Jika Feka meninggalkan Shah, bererti Fika memberi peluang kepada gadis itu. Irwan juga memaklumkan yang Shah sengaja merancang supaya Feka tidak ke Perth. Apabila Feka mengajak makan tengah hari, Faris mengaturkan agar Shah makan dengan "client" wanita. Usaha Faris dan Shah masih tidak menjadi.

programme.title: Halalkan Hati Yang Ku Curi S1 Ep08
programme.desc: Nenda berbincang dengan ibu Delisha, tidak bersetuju Delisha berkahwin dengan Faiq. Alasan, Faiq tiada kerja dan suka berfoya-foya. Sikap Zainal masih berusaha mendekati keluarga Delisha. Akhir-akhir ini, Delisha berubah sedikit dengan melakukan kerja-kerja rumah. Apabila ustaz tidak setuju saranan nenda mengahwini Delisha, nenda akur alasan ustaz, tiba-tiba Delisha disetujuinya berkahwin Faiq. Lantaran itu majlis perkahwinan, mereka telah dilangsungkan. Turut diundang Salima dan Zainal. Mereka berdua ketika bertemu pasangan pengantin hanya berpura-pura megucapkan yang baik Bagi Zainal dia berdendam dan ada niatnya akan meruntukan rumah tangga Faiq dan Delisha. Sangkaan Daud dia tidak dijelas dengan tepat tentang syarikat ibu mertuanya. Mujur semakan disyarikat, nenda mendapati masih boleh bertahan , sedangkan nenda amat berhati-hati dia yang kena bayar. Kebetulan Delisha dan Faiq baru balik dari "Shopping", nenda terus menasihati mereka supaya berjimat cermat.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Sarakit dirogol empat lelaki bertopeng sementara seorang lagi, Ramdi, diminta menjaga di luar rumah. Keesokan hari, ibu bapa Sarakit pergi menjenguk Sarakit dan mendapati rumahnya berkunci dan tiada respon dari Sarakit. Mereka terserempak dengan Pak Bado yang mengadu bahawa Sarakit sudah sombong setelah berkahwin dengan Rafiq dan melanggar adat resam kampung. Sarakit yang sangat lemah dan tidak berdaya untuk bangun dan bersuara mendengar perbualan mereka. Sementara itu, Mariam masih enggan membenarkan Rafiq pulang ke Sarakit atas alasan dia sakit dan cuba mendekatkan Rafiq dengan Dina, bekas teman wanitanya. Pada masa yang sama, Ramdi sering diganggu oleh lembaga putih berambut panjang yang setiap malam merayau-rayau di kampung sambil menangis dan memohon maaf. Pada satu malam, Kiol, salah seorang yang merogol Sarakit, dicekik lembaga putih berambut panjang dan mayatnya dijumpai di sungai dengan jari kelingkingnya dipotong.

programme.title: Cicakman 3
programme.desc: Berlatarkan selepas 7 tahun acara Cicakman 2: Planet Hitam. Cicakman, bekas adiwira Metrofulus telah menghilangkan diri dengan orang mendakwa Cicakman sudah mati atau sudah bersara. Dalam ketiadaannya, adiwira baharu yang dikenali sebagai SuperBro telah muncul dan menjadi bekas pertahanan Metrofulus.

programme.title: Hantu Gangster
programme.desc: Di sebuah bandar kecil yang terletak di Klang, penyangak bernama Te Sai mencuri cincin semasa majlis peringatan gangster, tidak tahu bahawa ia adalah berhantu. Cincin itu menjadi tuan rumah hantu tiga bekas pemimpin geng yang mula menghantui Te Sai kerana dia membawa cincin mereka. Te Sai tidak lama lagi mendapati bahawa ketiga-tiga mereka telah dibunuh oleh pengkhianat yang peribadi agenda mengancam asas bagi segala perpaduan antara ketiga-tiga kumpulan. Berpandukan hantu, Te Sai kini perlu melakukan apa yang boleh untuk menyatukan kumpulan-kumpulan dan mengelakkan tragedi yang boleh menyebabkan kematian ramai yang tidak bersalah.

programme.title: Jamu Nesan S1 Ep12
programme.desc: Madam Zoora bengang dengan Madam Seow yang tidak habis-habis ingin menganggu bisnesnya. Madam Seow akhirnya menjadi orang tawanan Madam Zoora selepas Sunny Lee tidak lagi mahu melindunginya kerana disyaki menculik dan cuba membunuh Alvin. Madam Zoora meminta Madam Seow membawanya berjumpa dengan Sunny Lee kerana dia tahu di mana Alvin dan sanggup membantu Madam Seow mencari anak Sunny Lee tetapi sebagai balasan Madam Seow perlu membantu dia berkolaborasi dengan Sunny Lee. Madam Seow dengan angkuh tidak bersetuju dengan Madam Zoora. Madam Zoora panik kerana Alvin hilang dan Tok Chai mengesyaki bahawa ada orang dalam yang melepaskan Alvin. Akhirnya, Tok Chai ditembak oleh orang Madam Seow.

programme.title: Help! My House Is Haunted S3 Ep9
programme.desc: Kelly Tinggal di kotej abad ke-18 di pinggir Hutan Dekan. Selepas hanya setahun tinggal di hartanah itu, dia dan keluarganya memerlukan bantuan untuk menjelaskan sebab lampu menyala dan mematikan apabila arahan, roh lelaki berjalan di dalam dan di luar harta itu tetapi yang paling membimbangkan ialah perubahan mood misteri anak perempuan Kelly. Apabila keluarga berpindah ke harta itu, Kelly menemui beberapa abu di taman yang dia percaya adalah manusia. Adakah ini kunci kepada semua aktiviti paranormal? Pasukan itu dengan cepat mengenal pasti dua entiti lelaki; satu roh terperangkap tetapi yang mana satu dan mengapa?

programme.desc: Anak Jantan menceritakan kisah Darin yang dihantui oleh kehidupan yang lalu. Gaya hidup negatifnya berubah sama sekali apabila beliau jatuh cinta kepada seorang wanita dari kampungnya bernama Nara. Tidak lama kemudian, pasangan ini berhijrah ke bandar KL untuk memulakan kehidupan baru. Mereka dikurniakan seorang anak lelaki yang bijak bernama Saufi. Malangnya, kebahagiaan keluarga mereka tidak bertahan lama dengan ketibaan Somchai, seorang rakan lama yang kembali menyebabkan pergolakan di tempat kerja Darin.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep7
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Danial, bodyguard kepada Eliza memaklumkan kepada Nasha bahawa Eliza telah diculik. Amran melakukan perculikan tersebut untuk mendapatkan bayaran tebusan. Rashid dan Danial berjaya menyelamatkan Eliza, akhirnya Amran tertangkap. Azizah Ibu Rashid sebenarnya adalah bekas isteri kepada bapa Eliza. Ryan, bodyguard kepada Dato' Amir. programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Sarakit dirogol empat lelaki bertopeng sementara seorang lagi, Ramdi, diminta menjaga di luar rumah. Keesokan hari, ibu bapa Sarakit pergi menjenguk Sarakit dan mendapati rumahnya berkunci dan tiada respon dari Sarakit. Mereka terserempak dengan Pak Bado yang mengadu bahawa Sarakit sudah sombong setelah berkahwin dengan Rafiq dan melanggar adat resam kampung. Sarakit yang sangat lemah dan tidak berdaya untuk bangun dan bersuara mendengar perbualan mereka. Sementara itu, Mariam masih enggan membenarkan Rafiq pulang ke Sarakit atas alasan dia sakit dan cuba mendekatkan Rafiq dengan Dina, bekas teman wanitanya. Pada masa yang sama, Ramdi sering diganggu oleh lembaga putih berambut panjang yang setiap malam merayau-rayau di kampung sambil menangis dan memohon maaf. Pada satu malam, Kiol, salah seorang yang merogol Sarakit, dicekik lembaga putih berambut panjang dan mayatnya dijumpai di sungai dengan jari kelingkingnya dipotong.

programme.title: Anak Jantan
programme.desc: Anak Jantan menceritakan kisah Darin yang dihantui oleh kehidupan yang lalu. Gaya hidup negatifnya berubah sama sekali apabila beliau jatuh cinta kepada seorang wanita dari kampungnya bernama Nara. Tidak lama kemudian, pasangan ini berhijrah ke bandar KL untuk memulakan kehidupan baru. Mereka dikurniakan seorang anak lelaki yang bijak bernama Saufi. Malangnya, kebahagiaan keluarga mereka tidak bertahan lama dengan ketibaan Somchai, seorang rakan lama yang kembali menyebabkan pergolakan di tempat kerja Darin.

programme.title: Syurgaku Tak Sempurna 2 Ep10
programme.desc: Zalia terima gambar Tg Zarif dengan wanita lain dan mulai murung. Zalia pergi kerumah Jun dan pada masa yang sama, Puan Sri Suhana muncul kerana dia hantar Daniel balik ke rumah Jun. Zalia terkejut dan terus pergi. Jun kejar Zalia sehingga menyebabkan anaknya jatuh dalam pool.

programme.title: Ropes
programme.desc: Dengan kesedihan atas kematian kakaknya yang masih sangat baru-baru ini, Elena, seorang quadriplegic muda, telah bersara ke sebuah rumah negara bersama bapanya. Di sana dia mendapat bantuan Athos, seorang pastor Belgium yang dilatih khas untuk membantunya. Tapi makhluk yang seharusnya menjadi sahabatnya telah terkena penyakit aneh... dan telah berubah menjadi musuh terburuknya

programme.title: Syurgaku Tak Sempurna 2 Ep9
programme.desc: Hakimi memulakan siasatan keatas semua kes yang berlaku di tapak pembinaan Tengku Zarif. Zahid dapat tahu tentang rancangan jahat Zahir dan Fariesya untuk memisahkan Zalia dan Zarif. Jun pula buat keputusan yang dia tak nak bantu Fariesya, Fariesya menjadi marah dan ugut nak ambil semula Daniel dan Jun takkan dapat jumpa dia sampai bila – bila.

programme.title: Gerak Khas The Movie II
programme.desc: Inspektor Mazlan dan Inspektor Aleeza ditugaskan untuk menyiasat tentang satu sindiket penyeludapan dadah terbesar di Malaysia yang diketuai oleh seorang penjenayah yang bernama Raziman

programme.title: Syurgaku Tak Sempurna 2 Ep10
programme.desc: Zalia terima gambar Tg Zarif dengan wanita lain dan mulai murung. Zalia pergi kerumah Jun dan pada masa yang sama, Puan Sri Suhana muncul kerana dia hantar Daniel balik ke rumah Jun. Zalia terkejut dan terus pergi. Jun kejar Zalia sehingga menyebabkan anaknya jatuh dalam pool.

programme.title: Hantu Gangster
programme.desc: Di sebuah bandar kecil yang terletak di Klang, penyangak bernama Te Sai mencuri cincin semasa majlis peringatan gangster, tidak tahu bahawa ia adalah berhantu. Cincin itu menjadi tuan rumah hantu tiga bekas pemimpin geng yang mula menghantui Te Sai kerana dia membawa cincin mereka. Te Sai tidak lama lagi mendapati bahawa ketiga-tiga mereka telah dibunuh oleh pengkhianat yang peribadi agenda mengancam asas bagi segala perpaduan antara ketiga-tiga kumpulan. Berpandukan hantu, Te Sai kini perlu melakukan apa yang boleh untuk menyatukan kumpulan-kumpulan dan mengelakkan tragedi yang boleh menyebabkan kematian ramai yang tidak bersalah.

programme.title: Bisikan Iblis
programme.desc: Di sekolah semua perempuan, akan sentiasa ada kematian misteri setiap tahun, dan Nany didaftarkan di sekolah ini.

programme.title: Japanizi Going Going Gong Ep34
programme.desc: Peserta terperangkap dalam gelembung dan kemudian perlu memakai lampin sebelum meluncur menuruni bukit yang besar.

programme.title: Ular
programme.desc: Sekumpulan pemenang cabutan bertuah memenangi percutian impian di resort pulau yang kelihatan indah, hanya untuk mendapati diri mereka terperangkap di pulau yang dipenuhi ular maut.

programme.title: Permainan Cinta S1 Ep8
programme.desc: Dr Soraya curiga dengan tingah laku Safiah dan menyoal Safiah kerana masuk ke bilik Dr. Arman. Dr Soraya marahkan Safiah kerana masuk ke tempat yang tidak sepatutnya.Syifa cuba dekatkan diri dengan Dr Arman. Dia tahu Dr Arman berasal dari Kedah dan Syifa ci[ta satu persona@penyamaran sebagai gadis kampung dari Kedah, namun cara itu tidak membuahkan hasil. Ketika Dr Arman sibuk di makmal, Syifa cuba pikat dengan masakan nya. Dr Soraya sedar Dr.Arman semakin rapat dengan Syifa dan Safiah, dia telah sengaja buli mereka dan malukan mereka di depan Dr Arman. Syifa dan Safiah mula berpakat untuk kena kan Dr.Soraya depan semua staff.

programme.title: Puaka Balai Gombak
programme.desc: Ramai mempercayai bahawa sesebuah tempat atau lokasi itu dikatakan berpuaka setelah berlaku sesuatu tragedi yang melibatkan kematian atau kawasan yang telah lama ditinggalkan. Alam mistik sering menjadi sebuah topik yang subjektif dan menjadi perbalahan dikalangan masyarakat kerana masing-masing mempunyai perspektif yang berbeza-beza terutama sekali di kalangan ahli-ahli kumpulan paranormal di Malaysia mahupun di luar negara. Antara tempat-tempat yang sering menerima kunjungan kumpulan-kumpulan paranormal tempatan adalah seperti Balai Gombak, Highland Towers, Villa Nabila, Apartment Riviera II, Taman Rekreasi Mimaland di Gombak dan banyak lagi.

programme.title: Help! My House Is Haunted S2 Ep7
programme.desc: Mike dan Alison telah berada di kotej lama mereka yang indah selama 4 tahun. Dan gambar jatuh dari dinding, figura dan bayang-bayang berkelip melepasi tingkap (kanak-kanak), bintik-bintik sejuk di ruang tamu. Perkara utama yang kelihatan menarik aktiviti poltergeist ialah besi antik lama yang terus bergerak dan jatuh. Bolehkah pasukan itu mengenal pasti poltergeist, adakah besi itu dirasuk, dan adakah roh pelajar sekolah bermain di taman?

programme.title: Dendam Orang Mati
programme.desc: Lena merupakan isteri kepada Shahrul pernah terlantar di hospital kerana koma.Ketika dalam keadaan koma, suaminya telah berkahwin dengan perempuan lain bernama Min. Mereka kini tinggal di flat usang empat tingkat. Selepas tersedar daripada koma, Lena disahkan menghidap amnesia dan dia sering diganggu roh yang berniat untuk membalas dendam di atas kematiannya.

programme.title: Pontianak Harum Sundal Malam
programme.desc: Seorang primadona gamelan bernama Meriam tersepit di antara cinta dua lelaki: Danial dan Marsani. Meriam berkahwin dengan Danial dan perkara ini telah menimbulkan rasa cemburu kepada Marsani. Meriam kemudiannya ditemui mati ketika hamil anak sulungnya. Sejak itu, kampung terbabit tidak lagi aman apabila berlaku pelbagai kejadian yang menakutkan.

programme.title: Pontianak Harum Sundal Malam 2
programme.desc: Marsani mewasiatkan agar segala harta Meriam dipulangkan kepada warisnya namun ia tidak kesampaian apabila Maria menghilangkan diri. Meriam bersumpah untuk membalas dendam selagi miliknya tidak dipulangkan sepenuhnya. Dia kembali untuk menghantui seluruh keturunan Marsani. Satu hari, Bayang dan Joyo, seorang guru tarian kuda kepang di kampung itu ternampak Maria menjelma menjadi Meriam melalui semangat pontianak.

programme.title: Main- Main Hantu
programme.desc: Bas rosak ketika dalam perjalanan ke Melaka menyebabkan sekumpulan pemain bola jaring bersama jurulatih mereka terpaksa bermalam di sebuah banglo yang buruk. Di banglo itu, mereka bertemu penjaga tempat tersebut - pasangan yang sudah lanjut usia. Namun, gangguan misteri mula berlaku sejak kedatangan mereka di situ.

programme.title: Waris Jari Hantu
programme.desc: Tina mempunyai pertalian saudara dengan Tok Wan Rimau, penjaga harimau saka yang sedang mencari waris perempuan untuk menurunkan ilmu sakanya. Dalam masa yang sama, Tina mencintai Ari, seorang lelaki yang berperwatakan lembut. Walaupun dihalang keras oleh keluarganya, Tina memilih untuk menjadi pewaris saka Tok Wan, sehinggalah Ari menawarkan dirinya untuk menjadi pengganti

programme.title: Misteri Rumah Tua
programme.desc: Dendam lama mula terbalas apabila hadirnya sekumpulan remaja ke sebuah rumah lama yang dihuni roh wanita. Sebuah pembunuhan kejam telah berlaku di rumah tersebut apabila dia dirogol dan dibunuh ketika sedang sarat mengandung. Wanita tersebut ingin membalas dendam kerana ketidakadilan yang telah berlaku ketika dirinya masih hidup. Bapa kepada salah seorang dari kumpulan remaja tersebut pula pernah terlibat dengan pembunuhan kejam wanita itu yang menaikkan lagi rasa marah roh tersebut. Pelbagai insiden menyeramkan mula terjadi di rumah itu.

programme.title: Dendam Dari Pusara
programme.desc: Dolah, seorang buruh kasar yang cacat kaki sejak kecil mempunyai ilmu luar biasa yang diperolehinya dengan memotong dagu si mati dijadikan minyak tetapi perlu mematuhi syarat ketat dengan memulangkan barang-barang yang diperolehi dalam tempoh seribu hari. . Dolah melakukan kerja ngeri ini dengan bantuan dua orang kawannya, tetapi pada suatu masa dia telah gagal memenuhi syarat tersebut dan bermacam kejadian telah berlaku selepas itu.

programme.desc: Dihantui gangguan misteri, sepasang suami isteri mula mencari punca kepada gangguan tersebut. Namun tragedi melanda apabila Marina lemas di laut dan meninggal dunia - dari situlah bermulanya kejadian aneh.

programme.title: Setinggan
programme.desc: Kawasan setinggan yang dibangunkan di tapak kubur tali barut Jepun menimbulkan kekacauan terhadap penduduk di situ. Hantu-hantu kubur tersebut merayau dan menganggu ketenteraman penduduk di situ.

programme.title: Seri Dewi Malam
programme.desc: Cinta seorang isteri kepada suami yang sangat kuat membuatkannya ingin terus berjuang untuk hidup. Azri menemui jalan untuk berkomunikasi bersama isterinya, Seri yang jatuh koma. Dewi, seorang gadis buta yang memboleh membaca minda memutuskan untuk membantu Azri berhubung dengan Seri. Lama kelamaan, perasaan cinta mula muncul dan Azri harus membuat pilihan yang sukar.

programme.title: Karak
programme.desc: Empat orang pelajar kolej: Nik, Zura, Jack dan Ida yang sedang terperangkap dalam satu kesesakan jalan raya yang sangat teruk sepanjang berada di lebuhraya Karak telah membuat keputusan untuk keluar dari lebuhraya dan meneruskan perjalanan dengan melalui jalan lama. Mereka tidak mengetahui bahawa keputusan itu akan mengubah hidup mereka selamanya.

programme.title: Setinggan
programme.desc: Penduduk di suatu setingan diganggu hantu. Mereka berkerja sama untuk mencari jalan penyelesaian. Akhirnya mereka berjaya menghalau hantu daripada menggangu setinggan mereka.

programme.title: Den Budak Motor
programme.desc: Den Budak Motor mengisahkan tentang Deniel, seorang lelaki yang kecewa ditinggalkan oleh bekas kekasihnya, Sarah disebabkan kesusahan Deniel yang hanya memiliki motor kapcai.

programme.title: Tmo Gila Tak Cinta
programme.desc: Saksikan di sebalik tabir pembikinan Filem Gila Tak Cinta

programme.title: Leraian Mimpi
programme.desc: Zakiah telah mendapat tawaran sebagai pelakon drama dan di bawah bimbingan Sarah seorang pengarah terkenal, bakatnya telah berkembang dan telah dinobatkan sebagai pelakon wanita terbaik. seperti janjinya kepada ibunya, menjaga nama baik diri dan keluarganya meski pun ada usaha daripada pihak-pihak tertentu yang cuba mengheretnya ke kancah kontroversi.

programme.title: Seleksi Sinema Ep8
programme.desc: Seleksi lagu-lagu menarik untuk hiburan anda

programme.title: Mengemis Rindu
programme.desc: seorang ayah yang membesarkan sendiri anak-anaknya dengan penuh kasih sayang setelah kematian isteri. Namun, apabila anak-anak mempunyai kerjaya yang baik dan berumahtangga, mereka tidak lagi menjengah atau bertanya khabar ayahnya itu.

programme.title: Mau Jadi Apa?
programme.desc: Nordin menghantar pembulinya, Roy, ke hospital. Rudy pula ditangkap polis. 6 bulan kemudian, Nordin menjuarai rancangan kuiz yang selalu ditonton oleh banduan-baduan sesama Rudy. Rudy mengecam Nordin dan mula merancang cara melarikan diri dari penjara supaya dapat membalas dendam ke atas Nordin.

programme.desc: Seleksi lagu-lagu menarik untuk hiburan anda

programme.desc: Ara dan ibunya hanya mampu pasrah menghadapi kekejaman ayahnya. Ara yang sepatutnya masih menikmati keindahan zaman kanak-kanak, tetapi dia terpaksa mencari wang untuk ayahnya sendiri. Ara terpaksa menjual kuih mochi dan hasilnya adalah untuk ayahnya.

programme.title: Dewi Rindu Ep40
programme.desc: Dewi adalah seorang gadis yang mempunyai impian yang sangat besar. Dia berazam untuk menjadi seorang yang berjaya dan membawa keluarganya keluar dari kesempitan hidup. Namun siapa sangka, impian indahnya itu musnah malah terpaksa mengharungi realiti pahit iaitu hamil di luar nikah.

programme.title: D'Academy 5 Ep29
programme.desc: D'Academy kini kembali! D'Academy atau DA (singkatan dari Dangdut Academy) ialah pertunjukan bakat muzik dangdut yang pertama dan terbesar. Acara ini telah berjaya membangkitkan fenomena muzik dangdut, dan program ini telah menjadi salah satu pertunjukan pencarian bakat yang paling berjaya di Indonesia. Musim ini merupakan musim kelima dan diadakan buat kali pertama selepas tidak dihadirkan selama lima tahun.

programme.title: Biarkan Semesta Bekerja, Aku dan Kamu Love-Love-an Aja
programme.desc: Paula dalam perjalanan pulang dan hampir melanggar Baim dengan motosikalnya. Baim memutuskan untuk mengejarnya dan mengetahui di mana dia tinggal. Pada hari yang sama, Paula mendapati seorang bayi menangis di hadapan rumahnya. Secara kebetulan, ibu Paula pulang ke rumah dan salah faham dengan keadaan itu. Dia menyangka bayi itu milik Paula dan Baim.

programme.title: Taste of Life (T) Ep777778
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change… Chin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened. Chu-tsai’s second son Ying-kai has always set his goal to reach the top of his career. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.title: Stories In Taiwan (T) Ep924
programme.desc: In a playful and relaxed style, the host went deep into the corners of various towns and villages in Taiwan, looking for the uniqueness, introduced the special local customs and traditions.

programme.title: How to Pick Girls Up !
programme.desc: Xin, a helpless loser in love, calls in to a radio show hosted by DJ Tsang to ask desperately for help. A self-proclaimed love expert, Tsang takes it upon himself to make sure Xin meets girls and leads him on a series of absurd excursions into the wild and dangerous world of modern love.

programme.title: Naked Soldier
programme.desc: When Interpol agent Long busted a billion-dollar drug deal 15 years ago, the cartel took revenge and killed his family. The cartel boss, Madame Rose, even kidnaps and raises Long’s daughter, Phoenix, to become a skilled assassin. Only when Phoenix is about to kill Long did she discover the startling fact about her true identity…

programme.title: Touch of the Light
programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh. Their friendship grows as Siang and Chieh pursue their dreams together. Sandrine Pinna was awarded Best Actress for her role as Chieh in the 2012 Taipei Film Festival.

programme.title: Legend of the Naga Pearls
programme.desc: A thief and a constable team up to save humanity from creatures known as the Winged Tribe, who lost their power of flight centuries ago after their war against mankind. They are hell-bent on seeking revenge by obtaining a mystical artifact called the Naga Pearls.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963, and ruthlessly carved an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: Ready O/R Knot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi have been together for five years since they first met in a wedding banquet, but marriage soon becomes a challenge to their relationship. Heidi sees marriage as a testimony of their love, while Guy sees it as doomsday. Can the couple resolve their conflict? Are they ready or not?

programme.title: Divergence
programme.desc: Three men are going beyond what their jobs require them to do. An ill-fated police detective runs into a woman during his investigation on a money laundering case, a lawyer protects a corrupt businessman from law and a ruthless killer violates his code to get involved in a police investigation. These three men are thrown together by circumstance...

programme.title: Night and Fog
programme.desc: Following “The Way We Are”, this is based on a true story happening in Tin Shui Wai. It revolves around an older, unemployed Hong Kong man, his young Mainland wife and their two daughters. Their lives, unfortunately, are anything but easy, and the shocking conclusion raises issues about the plight of the socially deprived lower class.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s’ Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: Reunion Dinner
programme.desc: Chao Yang and Zi Hong are soon to wed but both have not met the other’s parents. When a client requests for a livestream of their reunion dinner to promote his products, it set the stage for their parents’ first meeting. Estranged from his mother, Yang decides to rent a family for the dinner which results in a series of mishaps and hilarity.

programme.title: All's Well End's Well 2011
programme.desc: Popular make-up artist Sammy is hired as the CEO of a cosmetics company which all staffs are women. Unfortunately, he is clueless with women so he invites Arnold, a fellow make-up artist, to join him. Though Arnold might appear to be a woman's magnet, his heart still lingers with his first love Mona.

programme.title: 3Ft Ball and Souls
programme.desc: Members of an internet suicide room called Life Club decide to end their lives using explosives. But every time the fireworks explode, they find themselves back-in-time before they carried out their plan. They suspect the cause of this mystery to be the young age of one of the members and tries to convince the high school girl to quit…

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: Mann, an accomplished police officer, has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, Mann is forced to return to his former glory when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: Seobok
programme.desc: Former secret agent Ki Hun is entrusted with a secret mission to escort the first human clone, Seobok, to a safe place. Seobok, who possesses a life-preserving DNA that could save humanity, explores the outside world with Ki Hun for the first time but they are both chased and claimed as terrorists by CIA. How can Ki Hun protect Seobok from danger?

programme.title: The Way We Dance
programme.desc: Tofu shop girl Fleur possesses a quirky gift for hip hop and dance which she uses to becomes a supernova in the university dance crew. Meanwhile, Alan, from the Tai Chi Club has an eye for Fleur's sleight of hand and tries to recruit her into his club.

programme.title: Driving Miss Wealthy
programme.desc: To teach his irresponsible daughter Jennifer some respect, her billionaire father pretends to disown her. He then hires Mario to pretend to be her driver and protect her. Just as the two start falling for each other, Jennifer’s father becomes very ill and she must take over his business. Will Jennifer and Mario’s budding romance continue?

programme.title: The Fatal Raid
programme.desc: Twenty years after a deadly bloodbath between the Hong Kong Police and Macau gangsters, Madam Fong, the surviving team member, leads a new squad of four policewomen across borders to pursue young anarchists terrorizing Macau in a mission to protect the Hong Kong Police’s Deputy Chief Commissioner.

programme.title: Fleet of Time
programme.desc: A coming-of-age tale about a group of close friends from high school, college and eventually reaching adulthood through the 1990s and 2000s. They meet again at a friend's wedding in 2014 and recall their romantic past through memories.

programme.title: Integrity
programme.desc: Anti-corruption senior officer Chen lines up a key witness, corporate accountant Jack, to testify against a tobacco trading company CEO for bribing high-level customs officer as well as smuggling contraband cigarettes. When neither Jack nor the CEO shows up on the day of the hearing, Chen must team up with his ex-wife to launch an investigation.

programme.title: Love is…Pyjamas
programme.desc: Underwear designer Spring and her daughter work at Hugo’s enterprise. Hugo demands a new fashion line design competition between Spring and the newly employed ex model Jojo to save his company from bankruptcy and the winner will take charge of the line. Who will win the competition and will Hugo’s enterprise be saved?

programme.title: New Police Story
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Wing is an elite in the police force but has been drowning his guilt in booze after his entire team was killed by the “Gang of Five” in a mission. A year later, a young rookie detective with a complicated background is assigned to partner Wing and manages to inspire him into action, as Wing vows to take down the gang.

programme.title: Golden Chicken 2
programme.desc: The sequel is set in 2046 when a 82-year-old Ah Kam stops a heartbroken young man from taking memory loss pills. To help ease his pain, Ah Kam shares her life stories from 2003, one of Hong Kong’s toughest year with SARS, including the different people she comes across and the bittersweet romance between herself and her cousin.

programme.title: Kung Fu Monster
programme.desc: In the Ming Dynasty, the Bruneian Empire offers a monster as a gift to the nation. Imperial guard Ocean is tasked to train it, but realizing it is a kind creature by nature, he releases it secretly so that it will not become a killing beast. His action prompts a frenzy hunt for the monster when the palace puts a hefty bounty for its return…

programme.title: Who Killed Cock Robin
programme.desc: An ambitious journalist eagerly pursues a long-forgotten accident. When the sole survivor of the accident suddenly disappears, he realizes that nothing is what it seems, and the unimaginable dark truth will haunt him for the rest of his life.

programme.title: Dealer Healer
programme.desc: Based on a true story, Dealer Healer follows the story of Chen Hua, a former underworld kingpin and drug dealer, who takes a new lease of life and help rehabilitate people from drug addiction.

programme.title: Justice, My Foot!
programme.desc: Chow stars as Sung, a lawyer who uses any means necessary to help his wealthy clients escape the law. Sung retires to the countryside when urged by his wife, but when Mrs Sung encounters a woman whose husband's death has been covered up by corrupted officials, Sung returns to the court for justice to be served.

programme.title: 77 Heartbreaks
programme.desc: Adam is upset after breaking up with Eva and has a drunken tryst with Mandy. He discovers Eva’s diary which recorded her 77 heartbreaking experiences with him. Adam finally realizes Eva is his true love and they resolve to start anew. However, when Eva stumbles across evidence of his affair with Mandy, will she be able to pardon him a 78th time?

programme.title: The Golden Monk
programme.desc: A monk realizes he is the reincarnation of Golden Child who was cast down from heaven to experience life and death a hundred times, as he broke a sacred rule by falling in love with a fairy, Jade. While his memories are erased, Jade refuses to forget their love and accumulates goodwill over a hundred reincarnations to end Golden Child’s suffering.

programme.title: The Bravest Escort Group
programme.desc: A band of courageous bodyguards is tasked with escorting the daughter of general, the concubine of the recently deceased Ming emperor Wu Sangui, and her son, who is the last hope of the Ming Dynasty, to safety.

programme.title: Shining Moment
programme.desc: After being sidelined by the gymnastics team, Yu quits and reinvents himself as a Latin dance instructor. Starting afresh, he begins to assemble a group of children to compete in the Latin dance competition. But can Yu, still facing his own insecurities, bring out the best in these children and let them shine on stage?

programme.title: Cold War
programme.desc: A hijacking of a police van occurs when the Police Commissioner is away from Hong Kong. Deputy Commissioner Lee leads a rescue operation code-named Cold War. Fellow Deputy Commissioner Sean moves to take control from Lee as he thinks Lee is emotionally affected by his son being held hostage, but the efforts end up threatening both their reputation.

programme.title: Cold War 2
programme.desc: Sean Lau is now the Police Commissioner after the successful rescue operation Cold War. However, the culprits from the past not only dodged justice but even escalated their actions and kidnapped Lau’s wife. He breaks every protocol to get her back, which puts him under investigation.

programme.title: Princess Iron Fan
programme.desc: As Monkey (Yueh Hua) and his gang make their way to the West through Fire Mountain, they ran into the evil Princess Iron Fan (Pat Ting Hung), Madam White Bone (Cheng Pei Pei) and her sexy sister (Lily Ho), and have to fight their way through.

programme.title: The Kid With The Golden Arm
programme.desc: The government hires Yang to escort a cargo of gold to a famine stricken area. The vicious Chi Sha gang, with one of their best fighters, Golden Arm, announce their intention to hijack it by killing one of Yang's employees. As Yang gathers his own team of reputable fighters to protect his cargo, are they strong enough to hold off Golden Arm?

programme.title: The Grand Substitution
programme.desc: In this Opera epic, a loyal Imperial Court servant gives up his own newborn son to save the prince from an evil official.

programme.title: Five Elements Ninjas
programme.desc: The "Venoms" were no more. After five years and more than a dozen films together, the only one of the original five who proved so successful for the director was the muscleman Lo Meng. But with just that one "venom" and his incredibly agile new star Cheng Tien-chi, he made this spectacular, internationally popular, favorite. Evil ninjas (who attack with, and from, fire, sun, wood, water, and the ground) brutally slaughter a noble Chinese kung-fu school's students. The one survivor finds a teacher and four students who are ninjitsu experts. The five graduates take revenge. With this strong structure and exceptional kung-fu choreography (from the star and co-star Chu Ke), Chang Cheh produced platinum. This film was one of the director's best of his superheroic, grand guignol period. By any name, it could be called, almost literally, "bloody good" entertainment!

programme.title: The Tiger And The Widow
programme.desc: The Liu Chia-liang trained Hui Ying-hung was considered the top action martial arts female star in the 1980s. It is her martial arts abilities that Michelle Yeoh tries to emulate. In The Tiger and the Widow, Hui Ying-hung is somehow mixed up in a salt smuggling ring that stinks of missing persons and rotten dilemmas.

programme.title: The Shaolin Avengers
programme.desc: Hu seeks to avenge his father who is being killed by the White-Browed Hermit and his gang. However, he fails in his attempt and is saved by Fang Shi Yu, a youth from Shaolin whose parents are also killed by the same villains. They learn and master the advanced Shaolin style kung fu, before Fang leads Hu and the Shaolin fellows to fight the enemies.

programme.title: Melody Of Love
programme.desc: Three young doctors pursue three hard-to-get beauties in this romantic film set in the 70s “a-go-go” era. They have no idea where to start and use Rock-paper-scissor method to match themselves with the girls. The tactics and tricks they use are hilarious and they have to reshuffle their plans when nothing leads to success!

programme.title: The Mighty One
programme.desc: Lung seeks five volumes of a renowned Kung Fu manual to gain invincibility. When he believes a martial arts school master possesses the volumes, he kills him and his daughter but leaves behind a young brother and sister. Years later, Lung loses two volumes and starts another bloody hunt but each attempt is interrupted by two mysterious warriors...

programme.title: Moods Of Love
programme.desc: This Song Dynasty period piece about how far one would go for love (or lust) has two tales. The first involves a devilish magistrate who tries to tempt a Buddhist monk out of his self-professed celibacy by hiring a pretty prostitute. The second is the tragic tale of an exploited young girl who is forced to work in an unscrupulous couple’s brothel.

programme.title: Temple Of The Red Lotus
programme.desc: Wang Yu plays a young guy, Wu, who heads off to Dragon Valley to meet his childhood friend, Lian Chu (Chin Ping), who was promised to be his bride. When he gets there, he finds out that the family of his bride might not be an entirely honest bunch of people. Wu wishes to take Lian Chu with him, so he has no choice but to fight against her family…

programme.title: The Emperor And The Minister
programme.desc: The ingenious imperial scholar Liu Yung always embarrasses Emperor Chien Lung with his quick wit and gift of gab. The emperor purposely sets him up to solve the seemingly unsolvable. However, Liu Yung resolves it easily with wit and style and foils the emperor’s plot once again.

programme.title: The Twin Swords
programme.desc: Wang Yu plays Kwei Wu, who stumbles onto a kidnapping with his wife Kan Lien-chu (Chin Ping) at the Red Lotus Temple. Kan sends Kwei to go for reinforcements while she stays to fight the kidnappers, but she is captured and imprisoned in an iron cage. As Kwei returns with reinforcements, he must also race to the temple to save his wife.

programme.title: Return Of The Sentimental Swordsman
programme.desc: One of Shaw Studio’s highest grossing movies ever, this is the story of Li Chin Huan, the renowned, charming and sentimental swordsman who must fight many opponents, including an evil Clan Chief, for a place in the martial arts world.

programme.title: The Comedy Of Mismatches
programme.desc: Two pairs of lovers got mismatched accidentally. The man disguises as a woman for his sister’s wedding ceremony, while his lover disguises as a man to marry another woman. After the marriage mismatches are revealed, the lovers and their families are taken to court, where Prefecture Chief Qiao manages to work out a happy ending.

programme.title: Demon Of The Lute
programme.desc: Lute demon Chin Mo has reappeared in the world to wreak havoc. Hsiao Feng Ling is ordered to help find a special bow and arrows that can counter the demon. Only Chiao Yin knows the whereabouts of the weapon. Hsiao and her classmate Old Naughty set out on an arduous journey to find Chiao. After overcoming many obstacles, they catch Chin Mo's man trying to snatch the bow and manage to stop him in time....

programme.title: Call Of The Sea
programme.desc: A young fisherman, Chin Hu is in love with his childhood friend Hsiao Yu. However, the only son of a town bully lusts after Hsiao Yu’s beauty and tries all possible ways to approach her. Chin Hu protects another woman from the bully one day, leading Hsiao Yu to misunderstand him and suspect that they are having an affair...

programme.title: Five Superfighters
programme.desc: A kung fu master and his three students lost everything after they are floored by a bully. To take revenge, the students find ways to learn from other kung fu masters and come back six months later to have a rematch with the bully.

programme.title: Mr Funny - Bone
programme.desc: In this charming live-action adaptation of the beloved Old Master Q aka Mr Funny-bone, he and his sidekick, Mr. Potato get tangled in love when Mr Funny-bone falls head over heels in love with a dashing lady.

programme.title: Pursuit
programme.desc: This movie tells the tale of Lin Chong, the Sung Dynasty’s Chief Army Instructor who is framed by a corrupt official and has to embark on an exile fraught with danger. Helped by a monk, Lin Chong is finally able to take revenge.

programme.title: The Millionaire Chase
programme.desc: It's a fun and wild romp that mixes pleasure with pleasure. A nightclub owner, playboy Peter Chen Ho, has his ways with three sisters while gallivanting across Asia. Each one has a dangling relationship to save - ensuring a series of mishaps and comic moments.

programme.title: The Sentimental Swordsman
programme.desc: Li Xun Huan is a sentimental swordsman who has lived peacefully outside the martial arts world for the past 10 years. He returns home after knowing that the Plum Blossom Bandit is back to his old tricks, only to find that everything has changed.

programme.title: We Love Millionaires
programme.desc: In this romantic comedy, three beautiful Hong Kong salesgirls travel to Osaka in Japan to pursue their dreams of marrying a rich man. They masquerade as high society debutantes and make their way to a posh resort to meet and woo millionaires (or fake ones!).

programme.title: What Price Honesty
programme.desc: In this period martial arts thriller, three police graduates are assigned to a town rife with crimes and corruption. They vow to uphold justice but are hampered by their corrupt superior, resulting in them putting their lives and the lives of their beloved in danger.

programme.title: The Younger Generation
programme.desc: A tragic tale about a young girl who gets married and has five kids. When she and her husband die, leaving all five kids behind to fend for themselves, the eldest child is forced to be sold into prostitution to feed the other four.

programme.title: The Water Margin
programme.desc: This is a martial arts epic directed by Chang Cheh. In the Sung Dynasty, the government is run by corrupt officials, so Sung Jiang gathers 108 outlaws at Mount Liang and establishes a band of patriotic heroes to end the repression of brutal overlords.

programme.title: Na Cha The Great
programme.desc: Adapted from a chapter of the classic Chinese legend “Investiture of the Gods”, this is the story of Na Cha set 3000 years ago. After Na Cha sacrificed his life to save his parents, he is reincarnated with his spirit embodied in a lotus flower and is armed with two magic weapons to save the people from their despotic emperor.

programme.title: Bat Without Wings
programme.desc: The Bat Without Wings, a notorious rapist-murderer, has returned after a five-year absence. A young swordsman and a convoy master investigate the case and suspect that the Bat may be framed. A saying goes that a treasure map is hidden under the Bat’s knife, so they try to use that to hunt the real culprit…

programme.title: River Of Tears
programme.desc: Retired singer Fang lives happily with her husband and son. Tragedy happens when a man from her past returns to haunt her. In an ensuing struggle to free her from his clutches, her husband dies in a car accident. Blamed by her father-in-law for her husband’s death, Fang gets chased out of the house and goes back to singing to make a living...

programme.title: The Magnificent Swordsman
programme.desc: The Magnificent Swordsman centres on the hero who vows vengeance against evil bandits who killed his family when he was a child. The hero recruits several friends to help the peasants rid their village of marauding bandits, the leader of the band being the man who killed his family.

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: This is an epic tale set during the time of the Sino-Japanese war. A painter Yu saves a young girl, Lotus, who is being sold to a brothel. They fall in love, get married and settled in to a peaceful life. However, their life is soon shattered by the Japanese invasion and the brutal regime that follows.

programme.title: That Fiery Girl
programme.desc: The bandits of Hulu Valley slay the chief of the Mei Clan while searching for a treasure map. In retaliation, Chun from the Mei Clan infiltrates the bandit's fortress to map a way in for the authorities, but ends up falling in love with the bandit leader's daughter, Pearl. While Chun’s plot is uncovered, he receives unexpected help from Pearl.

programme.title: The Adventures Of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung travels incognito to Jiangnan to review his people’s livelihood but soon discovers that corrupt officials are oppressing his people. The emperor meets an upright young man and they join hands to teach the corrupt officials a lesson. The young man was appointed as his bodyguard thereafter.

programme.title: Dirty Ho
programme.desc: Master Wang, who is actually the 11th prince, poses as an antique connoisseur to hide his true identity. When he meets Dirty Ho, a witty con artist, Wang knows he has found the right man to help him untangle a royal succession plot...

programme.title: A Maid From Heaven
programme.desc: The seventh daughter of the Jade Emperor is banished from heaven to live a mortal life as she is very mischievous. She falls in love with a young village lad Yong, who sold himself to work for the rich so as to bury his father. The goddess sisters help Yong to pay his debt so the lovebirds can be together. Is this going to end happily-ever-after?

programme.title: Oath Of Death
programme.desc: Three Sung loyalists become blood brothers to fight the tyranny of the Tartar invaders. To oust the oppressors altogether, Ma releases the kidnapped Tartar princess in a strategic effort to gain points with the invaders, but it soon becomes apparent that he desires both a great position and power, and will do anything to get it…

programme.title: Godfather
programme.desc: When his son is in dire need of a heart transplant, a dreaded gangster tracks down the name of a suitable donor and eventually finds a boy. Consequently, the boy's family must fight to stay alive.

programme.title: Vanavarayan Vallavarayan
programme.desc: Vanavarayan and Vallavarayan are two brothers who share a strong bond. Problems arise when Vanavarayan meets Anjali, a beautiful girl, at a wedding and falls in love with her.

programme.title: Vanamagan
programme.desc: Kavya, a rich girl, goes to a restricted area in Andaman to celebrate the New Year with her friends. While evading the forest officers in the jungle, she knocks Jara, a tribal man, with her car.

programme.title: Wild Dog
programme.desc: A series of deadly attacks occur that pose a threat to national security. In response, a brash but brilliant intelligence agent leads a covert operation to find the perpetrators.

programme.title: Krack (Ravi Teja)
programme.desc: When three notorious criminals lock horns with a hot-tempered police officer, Potharaju Shankar, little do they know that they will end up behind bars.

programme.title: Varappogum 24 Manikkul
programme.desc: Three fugitives barge into a couple's house while escaping the authorities. However, they are flummoxed after finding the wife concealing a murder that has transpired in her home.

programme.title: Dora
programme.desc: Ignoring her misgivings, a young woman purchases a vintage car, which seems to have a mind of its own. Further investigation reveals that it is possessed by a vengeful spirit with ties to her past.

programme.title: Freeticket
programme.desc: The host presents a comprehensive compilation of songs and snippets from some of the most popular and trending Tamil movies.

programme.title: Saaho
programme.desc: An undercover agent and his partner go after a thief who has stolen 2,000 crore rupees. Soon, they realise that the case is linked to the death of a crime lord and an emerging gang war.

programme.title: Endrendrum Punnagai
programme.desc: Goutham grows up hating women after his mother abandons him during his childhood. Though he decides to stay single while his friends marry, Priya changes his mind about singlehood.

programme.title: Thalaivi
programme.desc: A biopic on the late Tamil Nadu Chief Minister J Jayalalithaa.

programme.title: Aan Devathai
programme.desc: Difficulties arise when Elango and Jessie, a married couple and parents of twins, decide to lead separate lives owing to an ugly fight.

programme.title: Brother'S Day
programme.desc: When Mani, a lineworker who is unhappy in his marriage, manages to make a time machine work due to an accident, he goes back in time to change his life.

programme.title: Sreekaram
programme.desc: Karthik, a young IT professional, works in a reputed firm and earns a hefty salary. However, he soon quits his job in order to pursue farming and promote agriculture among the youth.

programme.title: Sathura Adi 3500
programme.desc: Karuna, a police officer, sets out to investigate the suspicious death of a young man, Stephen. But trouble begins when he gets terrorised by Stephen's ghost.

programme.title: Pattathu Yaanai
programme.desc: Saravanan and his friends, with their new boss Gouravam, come to Trichy to set up a new restaurant. Their plans get messed up when Saravanan falls for Aishwarya, who is also pursued by a gangster.

programme.title: Thunder
programme.desc: After CBI officer Bose recovers from a coma, people start to address him by a different name. However, he soon realises that this is a plot by the state CM to seek revenge for an old rivalry. How Bose rediscovers his past and identity forms the rest of the story.

programme.title: Maapla Singam
programme.desc: Mapla Singam is a rural comedy about two families in a village that are in constant conflict with each other.

programme.title: Devi 2
programme.desc: Devi starts suspecting her husband, Krishna, of infidelity when she notices him with two other women. However, she unearths a horrifying truth when she decides to investigate.

programme.title: Junga
programme.desc: Junga is involved in a fight, because of which his family loses the theatre that they own. In order to get it back, he devises a plan that takes him to Paris, where he fights a criminal gang.

programme.title: Desingu Raja
programme.desc: A love story with boy and girl from feuding villages.

programme.title: Kappal
programme.desc: Vasu and his friends take a vow to never marry to keep their friendship intact. However, when Vasu falls in love with Deepika, his friends decide to ruin his affair.

programme.title: Balle Valleyatheva
programme.desc: Sakthi moves to a new village after his mother, who is a postmaster, gets transferred. He befriends a childless couple and falls in love with Thanikodi, a butcher's daughter.

programme.desc: Survival in the forest means maintaining a delicate balance between growth and destruction and death and rebirth - a forest should be in a constant state of regeneration. programme.title: Ol Pejeta Diaries 3 - Arc of Baringo Ep2

programme.title: Wildlife Icons 2 - Living Together Ep5
programme.desc: A complex web of relationships rules all life on earth: all species are interconnected, none can survive in isolation. While some relationships are one-sided, others are mutually beneficial. From loose associations to tight-knit partnerships, everything has a place in nature’s great scheme. Complex interactions between species are not even limited to animals, and some of the best examples occur in the lush mountain forests of Africa.

programme.title: Wild Rockies 1 - The Waterways Ep3
programme.desc: Some of mightiest rivers in North America originate on the glacial heights of the Rocky Mountains. The lakes, rivers and marshes of the Rockies are like arteries pulsing through the landscape, feeding the creatures that call the mountains home. Fed by glaciers and motivated by gravity, these waterways are split by the massive Rockies, which divert flow into the Atlantic, Pacific, and Arctic Oceans. From the uninhabitable icy pecks, water melts off glaciers, runs down thunderous waterfalls, filters through wetlands, sculpts the terrain, and finally flows out to the ocean, sustaining life and transforming environments along the way.

programme.desc: As fall sweeps across America and trees are set ablaze with color, animals are faced with make-or-break decisions. Find out how bald eagles, beavers, and other creatures prepare for the colder, darker, and leaner months ahead.

programme.title: Ol Pejeta Diaries 3 - Flight of the Pachyderms Ep3
programme.desc: The vets encounter a difficult predicament when a large elephant wanders off and ends up in a local village in an agitated state. If they can’t find a helicopter to help with herding immediately, they will have to have the elephant shot.

programme.title: Wild Rockies 1 - The Waterways Ep3
programme.desc: Some of mightiest rivers in North America originate on the glacial heights of the Rocky Mountains. The lakes, rivers and marshes of the Rockies are like arteries pulsing through the landscape, feeding the creatures that call the mountains home. Fed by glaciers and motivated by gravity, these waterways are split by the massive Rockies, which divert flow into the Atlantic, Pacific, and Arctic Oceans. From the uninhabitable icy pecks, water melts off glaciers, runs down thunderous waterfalls, filters through wetlands, sculpts the terrain, and finally flows out to the ocean, sustaining life and transforming environments along the way.

programme.title: Wild Rockies 1 - Balancing the Forest Ep4
programme.desc: Survival in the forest means maintaining a delicate balance between growth and destruction and death and rebirth - a forest should be in a constant state of regeneration. When trees get too tall they block all the sunlight from hitting the ground, which means grasses and smaller shrubs can’t grow, diminishing habitat for animals like elk, moose, caribou, and wolves.

programme.title: Planet Shark 1 - Ultimate Predator Ep1
programme.desc: Stalk the seas with sharks as they hunt using heightened senses and killer instincts. Watch a whitetip reef shark put its electrical sensors to work finding its prey’s heartbeat, and the pelagic thresher shark stun its quarry with its whiplike tail.

programme.title: The Ocean's Greatest Feast
programme.desc: Get a front-row seat to the planet’s biggest biomass migration, the annual 1,000-mile sardine run along South Africa’s east coast. See billions of these tiny fish run a gauntlet of hungry predators, including stealthy seals and dive-bombing gannets.

All's going well until Pat hits bumpy ground and the cable rolls out of the back of the jeep and back down the hill! Attempts to shout instructions to Ajay fail, but Pat realises Cedric could be the solution. The brave bird takes an instruction leaflet up to Ajay - who is then able to control the boots (using his toes) with ease! Meera, Julian and the others are delighted as Ajay touches down at Greendale School with the help of Cedric - the most welcome bird Ajay has ever watched!
